在 2008 年 11 月，她與製片夥伴潔西卡·羅絲（Jessica Rose）共同創辦一間新的媒體工作室 Webutantes。<ref>{{cite news |title=Jessica Rose and Taryn Southern Team Up As ‘Webutantes’ |url=http://news.tubefilter.tv/2008/11/18/jessica-rose-and-taryn-southern-team-up-as-webutantes/ |work=[[Tubefilter_News|Tubefilter News]] |date=2008-11-18 |accessdate=2008-12-09 |archive-date=2008-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211203725/http://news.tubefilter.tv/2008/11/18/jessica-rose-and-taryn-southern-team-up-as-webutantes/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

